            </a>
            <p class="brand-desc">
                A Bumiputera-owned strategic communication agency specializing in premium video and graphic production from conceptualization to polished post-production.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Quick Links</h4>
            <nav class="footer-nav">
                <a href="/about">About Us</a>
                <a href="/clients">Our Clients</a>
                <a href="/#work">Portfolio</a>
                <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Our Services</h4>
            <nav class="footer-nav">
                <a href="/photography">VIP & Corporate Photography</a>
                <a href="/videography">Video Marketing</a>
                <a href="/videography">Documentaries</a>
                <a href="/videography">Broadcast Setup</a>
            </nav>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-col">
            <h4>Headquarters</h4>
            <address class="footer-contact">
                No 22A, Jalan 7/23E Taman Danau Kota<br/>
                Setapak 53000 Wilayah Persekutuan<br/>
                Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
            </address>
            <div class="contact-links" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                <a href="mailto:fabareelkreatif@gmail.com">fabareelkreatif@gmail.com</a>
                <a href="tel:+601163623282">+60 11-6362 3282</a> 
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer-bottom">
        <div class="footer-bottom-container">
            <p>&copy; {currentYear} Fabareel Kreatif Sdn. Bhd. (1399599-T). All Rights Reserved.</p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Instagram">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect><path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path><line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line></svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://facebook.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Facebook">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path></svg>
                </a>
                <a href="https://youtube.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="YouTube">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22.54 6.42a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94-2C18.88 4 12 4 12 4s-6.88 0-8.6.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0-1.94 2A29 29 0 0 0 1 11.75a29 29 0 0 0 .46 5.33 2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94 2c1.72.46 8.6.46 8.6.46s6.88 0 8.6-.46a2.78 2.78 0 0 0 1.94-2 29 29 0 0 0 .46-5.33 29 29 0 0 0-.46-5.33z"></path><polygon points="9.75 15.02 15.5 11.75 9.75 8.48 9.75 15.02"></polygon></svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

<style>
    .site-footer {
        background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.5);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        padding-top: 4rem;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
        margin-top: 4rem;
    }

    .footer-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1.5fr;
        gap: 3rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
        .footer-container {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .footer-container {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
    }

    /* Brand Column */
    .brand-group {
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .brand-text {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: white;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    
    .brand-text .accent {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-left: 4px;
    }

    .brand-desc {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        max-width: 350px;
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* Columns Setup */
    .footer-col h4 {
        color: white;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    .footer-nav {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer-nav a, .contact-links a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
        display: inline-block; /* Allows transform */
        width: fit-content;
    }

    .footer-nav a:hover, .contact-links a:hover {
        color: white;
        transform: translateX(4px); /* Adds a nice little slide effect on hover */
    }

    .footer-contact {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        font-style: normal;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .contact-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.4rem;
    }

    /* Bottom Copyright Bar */
    .footer-bottom {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        margin-top: 4rem;
        padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .footer-bottom-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 2rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .footer-bottom-container p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .social-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1.2rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .social-links a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        transition: color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .social-links a:hover {
        color: white;
        transform: translateY(-3px); /* Gentle float effect matching your other site animations */
    }
</style>